#Text=Super Bowl XLVII : Ravens defeat 49ers , 34-31
#Text=Tuesday , February 5 , 2013
#Text=Joe Flacco from the Baltimore Ravens .
#Text=Image : Kevin B. Moore .
#Text=Baltimore Ravens
#Text=34
#Text=31
#Text=San Francisco 49ers
#Text=In the National Football League , the Baltimore Ravens defeated the San Francisco 49ers , 34 – 31 to win Super Bowl XLVII on Sunday , despite a power outage at the New Orleans Superdome .
#Text=Referee Jerome Boger flipped the coin and the Ravens of the AFC won the coin toss and elected to defer till the second half .
#Text=The 49ers of the NFC started on the 20 yard line and quickly went three and out .
#Text=The Ravens first play on offense was a pass from quarterback Joe Flacco to Vonta Leach for an 8 yard gain .
#Text=After working their way down the field the Ravens scored on a Flacco pass to Anquan Boldin .
#Text=Justin
#Text=Tucker
#Text=put in the extra point for the Ravens to take the lead 7 – 0 .
#Text=The 49ers came back on the next drive and drove down the field for a David Akers 36 yard field goal .
#Text=Nearing the end of the first quarter the Ravens were pushing towards a touchdown until they were stopped on a 3rd and 13 .
#Text=The next possession for the 49ers ended with a fumble by LaMichael James that was recovered by Arthur Jones for no gain .
#Text=After going down down the field , the Ravens scored on a Flacco pass to Dennis Pitta .
#Text=The next possession for the 49ers ended as soon as it started after a Colin Kaepernick interception by Ed Reed .
#Text=After the play penalties for unnecessary roughness were granted to each team due to an incident on the field .
#Text=Ted Ginn , Jr. from the San Francisco 49ers .
#Text=Image : BrokenSphere .
#Text=The Ravens worked their way down the field until they hit the 14 yard line , where they set up for a field goal .
#Text=Tucker took a direct snap and ran towards the first down marker ending up short of the first down ending their drive .
#Text=The ensuing 49ers drive ended in a 3 and out .
#Text=The Ravens responded with a 3 play touchdown drive ending with a 56 yard pass to Jacoby Jones from Flacco .
#Text=This put the Ravens up 21 – 3 with 1:45 left in the first half .
#Text=A successful 27 yard field goal by Akers followed shortly after as the score became 21 – 6 heading into halftime .
#Text=After the half-time show featuring Beyoncé , the Ravens got the ball to start the second half .
#Text=Akers kicked it off to Jacoby Jones , Jones stepping out from the end of the end zone returning it for 108 yards , an tie for the longest return in Super Bowl history .
#Text=This pushed the score up to 28 – 6 .
#Text=After a punt by the 49ers and the Ravens , the 49ers drove down the field to score with a 31 yard throw to Michael Crabtree for a touchdown .
#Text=An Akers extra point brought the score to 28 – 13 .
#Text=The next drive for the Ravens ended in a 3 and out .
#Text=The 49ers came back 2 plays later with a 6 yard run by Frank Gore .
#Text=The following Akers extra point made the score 28 – 20 .
#Text=The next possession for the Raven ended 2 plays in after a Ray Rice fumble that was recovered by Tarell Brown .
#Text=The next drive almost ended in a missed 39 yard field goal by Akers but was saved due to a running into the kicker penalty by Chykie Brown .
#Text=After the 5 yards were accessed , Akers lined up and made the 34 yard field goal bringing the score to 28 – 23 .
#Text=The Ravens responded on their next drive with a 19 yard field goal by Tucker to increase their lead to 31 – 23 .
#Text=The 49ers responded with a 5 play touchdown drive ending with a Kaepernick 15 yard scramble to close the gap to 31 – 29 with the extra point to follow .
#Text=The 49ers attempted a two point conversion but the pass was overthrown resulting in a missed attempt , leaving the score at 31 – 29 with 9:57 remaining in the 4th quarter .
#Text=The Ravens took over the ball for a 5 minute 38 second drive that ended in a Tucker 38 yard field goal , making the score 34 – 29 .
#Text=Trying to finish their rally , the 49ers drove down to the 7 yard line .
#Text=After a 2 yard rush by James , and 3 incomplete passes by Kaepernick , the Raven took over on downs on the 5 yard line with 1:46 left in the game .
#Text=After a run by Ray Rice , the 49ers called their last timeout to stop the clock with 1:42 left .
#Text=A run by Bernard Pierce , and then Leach left the Ravens with a 4th and 7 .
#Text=The Ravens called a timeout to determine their next play .

#Text=Lining up in punting formation , Koch caught the ball and ran around the end zone to waste time before getting pushed out for a safety by Chris Culliver to make the score 34 – 31 with 4 seconds left in the game .
#Text=To end the game Koch punted the ball to Ted Ginn who returned the ball to end the game .
